ce the RP welfare ranges are in play, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 9 living_in_simulation → 10 two_envelope_welfare_skepticism" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1Vl1z6jYQ%2FSs7TDuFDCHGgd6GDg8kIR9Tbm8mlzbTCRlH2GusRpY8koxDc%2FPfu7KBQIAnjHd1dvfsWa3fahHGLBf2QkVY69VOTqDf78NYMy7BKgg1%2B29BD4WESe577Q4USotozrGAoh34wWnQCbrBWdD2oG6syqDtNRzERBLUwJg8zSxXEsKEEHvgQca0ChPOhANsn%2FnQhpjpgBVsESR5yqRZGXxgkqdMmMCoFIuE2ZXlFOLc5hqXB4KUWYs6KLhNgoibUOXScjlbuXdAqs33wdbplVd3HW4JxwKh1iHPQPC5O8tlYHiaC1aWtarBA1uoAOUchcowKFBQURiYF6TyQ27Sko8hCxNgH6RwAwzuFjah55gLBCL9w2xOwLqiWRSZJmikTnGJBpQuwTQeE5csRcqVG3pvE6xo%2FsUQPzIsMX6HUKWZMo6OtQOdlRESIr3ipkQzlsmICSURUpKCaMHzutPD%2BbNL1R3H1wxDSwfnTOQIKi4RPkTRKsHO0ViY5gvIXRh30OBmYT0Y3IJhMdoF1O8xKpSK4J6cmA6TRoVxPfxzeD8YDy9huoAZStTMYitbrHSIEbdbZB2RsUmdtlVKjk9CKrEuuaasAePY%2FRDZ6Bqh9IyYyjQ1XS9gSiFiahU9N%2BF8ePXtfkhMaCZKhAL5LHHaIV6EcpOR8Oeqf0LNpNIkHDjzfoaLW6grTVUfq%2Fg4ZTPJbR4hnH8bDy9cZUbl2R%2FchgnKSyYWd6j%2FMhH04W0iATJUmcAbFBlGa4vX8rouoNfqOh%2BSlpgiZXJNjXQQlYvXrny8tnMqlY46ZqHNmThn8uXvsl%2FO9fRApKM90EdQb8PxIbjGRL5P5CzaKsTl4nWWyXj%2BRLI03nE4XVbk%2BZQu4%2BmOw6oan2q2idiyt1u%2Bs3a%2BEJtFtm3yPc%2FZvnQoiYksuIim%2Bcxs%2B%2Fxa%2Bfzmlz5MiBh3S%2FDXlOtKn588SrtD8JYaGz4Wl4PRP8DmqN2AZCT8n556m1KLtmRoeboc2g%2BZhYqMJEKU9tNg0XH26TaFLLfGqZlbJ6xQuYHuw6Pr7xsQ79iDSW2kQpKmkx28VLqb1JpQROtyepAik%2FW9wmyQAtrw3tyGvOZzrEZKLPaDbWriMMYD6Q3czqByNHd3weDrVWM%2F4paK9kMObr%2FCCVwssYbSaszoosNcm4RnB2A3tbcfdkwdunGbAmGEbJbjfqQtlTokmrRTfwfte0L3TQYP1YKAO63%2BJR4PtGRT3RUk6a3d7e6gPpDQaXkYgjJQT6psM7qFSUsRmgOc7o6HC%2BLjsbcbYTAaXQ0vD5D4aYSqVPc16PClvx95Z%2FY2oZ%2Fc5Gm6jNxu68OIG9vSSONnsF7%2BMUrb80W9mowmvP14%2FQGvrY0o7w26wqZuWfVhCfToPS0Herx33Y1vbr9%2FTGUPys8STqxPVzuP5p1TFoZmcmODUgTnsRl9Imvv%2FwNzXjiN" id="w1_2_3_4_5_9_10"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#d7c6e6;strokeColor=#6a3fa0;fontColor=#2c1650;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="1205" y="717" width="244" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Person-affecting&lt;br&gt;view&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+4+5+9+10+11]&lt;br&gt;→ The Humane League&lt;br&gt;(Jan Narveson, Melinda Roberts)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + living_in_simulation + two_envelope_welfare_skepticism + person_affecting_view&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Person-affecting population ethics: making happy people is neutral, so the astronomical case for x-risk reduction — which rests on the sheer number of extra future lives saved from extinction — loses almost all its force. Only the harm to people who exist regardless still counts. This is the standard premise longtermism&#x27;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 9 living_in_simulation → 10 two_envelope_welfare_skepticism → 11 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1Vu9z4jYQ%2FVd2mHZKMoTYTrhr6PCBJOTHHNfL5GgznZBxhL3G6smSR5JxaC7%2Fe1c2EAjwzWFXb3ffvifltRFjwgphL1SMjW7j%2BBh6vR6MNOMSrIJIs%2F%2Fm9FFKGBeB559CqbSIZxxLKP0wCE%2FC07ATnoW%2BF%2Fo%2BNI1VOfj%2BgUMZS0LrG1NkueVKQpQSaBc8yJlWUcqZcJj%2BWQA%2BJEyHrGTzMC0yJs0yEACTPGPChEZlWKbMLiMnkBS20Lg4EGbMWtRhyW0axtxEqpCWy%2Bky%2FRSkWv893Di9zOqsyi3gWCjUquQZCD5zZ7kMDc8KwaqxljN4YEsVopyhUDmGJQoaCkPzA2n8iJtslelDjtooGbIkwahqxxFa8TVgUQrsnTRugMHd3Kb0nXCBQHt5D5tjsI4UFsemBRppmVyiAaUrMI1HxDXLkGbhhn63KdZr%2BM0QfzKqMP6ASGW5Mo6uVQKdlTESIv3ETYVmLJMxE0oiZKQW0YbnlRgGs2fXqjuOLzkNRQdnTBQIKqkQ3nXTrsDO0ViYFHMoXBl30OD6YF0YEdaNWw%2FCENm0wPrg9