7;s critics deny (discussed as the key objection in Greaves &amp; MacAskill&#x27;s &#x27;The Case for Strong Longtermism&#x27;). It requires no_discounting_future_humans, the astronomical-stakes move it pushes back on. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 10 two_envelope_welfare_skepticism → 11 person_affecting_view" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1Vu9z4jYQ%2FVd2mHYKGUJsJ%2FR6dPhAEvJjyvUyOdpMJ2QcYa%2BxerLkkWQcmsv%2F3pUNBAJ8c9jV292370l5bcSYsELYCxVjo9c4OYF%2Bvw9jzbgEqyDS7L8FfZQSJkXg%2BWdQKi3iOccSSj8MwtPwLOyGvhf6PjSNVTn4fsthTCRhDYwpstxyJSFKCbIHHuRMqyjlTDhE%2F3MAPiRMh6xkizAtMibNKhAAkzxjwoRGZVimzK4ip5AUttC4PBBmzFrUYcltGsbcRKqQlsvZKv0MpNr8Pdw6vcrqrsst4Vgo1Lqk74EtVYhyjkLlGJYoqG0MzXekASNusnWmDzlqo2TIkgSjqqAjrGJkyKIU2Dst3ACDu4VN6TvhAoF4fw%2BbE7BubBbHpg0aaVlcogGlKzCNx8Qmy5C65YZ%2BtynWRP9iiCEZVRi%2FQ6SyXBlHyDqBzsoYCZF%2B4qZCM5bJmAklETJSg%2BjA83rZw%2Fmza9Udx5echqKDcyYKBJVUCO%2B66FRg52gsTIsFFK6MO2hwc7AejAnrxi0AYYRsVmB98Hr45%2FB%2BMB5ewnQBM5SomcVOvljpD2Nutxg6omCbFmzrPhyJhFRhXXJNrQJWawBiGB37Ss%2BInlzTrvUCplQiof3RdxvOh1df74c0vmaiQiiRz1K3QSJDKOeIlD%2FXSxNqJpUmvcBn72e4uIWm0jTqsUqOMzaT3BYxwvnX8fCiRf0YVeR%2FcBulKC%2BZWNyh%2FsvE0IfXiQSSi8oF3qDIMV5HvI7XdQW9TtflkN7EFKmTa9qeg6hTPL%2FO8XyXVAkcdcIiWzBxzuT3v6sludTTA5WO9kAfQdOH40NwrYl8m8hZvDWI68U7WzbjBRPJsmQn4XQ5kRdQu4xnOwmraQKa2aZiK%2B53Ahc9%2B0Rslvl2KPA8F%2Ft0Rk1MZMlFPC1mZjvn1zrnt6DKYUIkuDtCsKacvFEq9TGjijsEb6mx4WN5ORj9A2yO2rmCrA8%2FPfU2pRZvydDybOnUd5lFioIkQpT2g5voOPtwiUJeWOPUzK0TVqSci%2Fvw6Pb7CsQ79mDSGKmIpOlkB99r3U0abSjj9Tg9yJDJ5l5htkgBPry1tyGv%2BRxrS4nFfrBNTRzGeCC9gXsqaBzN7QKagy9Xrf2IWyraDzm4%2FQIncLHEGkqrMafbDQttUp4fgN3U3n7YnftpP9KWSh0SOe002EH7ltJ9k8ND%2FWrAnVb%2FEo8HVrKp7hqS9OZ3uzuoDyR0ejEMQRlopnW3OV29pKUYzQFOd%2B3higR47O1WGIxGV8PLAyR%2BsJBDOd2PcguGJehWfV%2FbCu7pQWA6Sg%2F0uOO%2BbfAn5z5NF5J71Pow4sZ2NJIFDTarP4zS9nzRrN3RhtcfLz%2FgpbNR561F19jUvVJ9WAI9ek9LU4%2F3vnPjm9tv787sQfUfCSfmp6vHjjzPq