ting_future_humans. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 11 person_affecting_view → 12 resilient_foods_beat_agi" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1lm1z4jYQx7%2FKDtNOIUOIbUivR4cXeeCSTLleJkd70wkZR9hrrJ4seSQ5Ds3lu3dlA4Fg3jns6rdP%2F5Xy0ooxYYWwFyrG1rB1cgKj0QimmnEJVkGk2X9L%2BiglzIrA8wdQKi3iJ44llH4YhP1wEJ6Gvh%2F6AbSNVTn4QccxZpJYZ8YUWW65khClhByCBznTKko5E47ofwzAh4TpkJVsGaZFxqRZGwJgkmdMmNCoDMuU2bWlD0lhC42rA2HGrEUdltymYcxNpAppuVys3Qcg1fbv4c7ptdfpJtwKx0KhNiF9H3LURsmQJQlGFaZqw9oegEbDBUdpw0Sp2IRzZDZkC161YsyiFNhbP7gBBrdLm9J3wgUCNfzNbE7AunpZHJsugWlKXKIBpSuYxmNqI8uQ0uSGfrcp1h3%2BxVBrZFQxfodIZbkyrhMbBzorYyQi%2FcRNRTOWyZgJJREykoHoweNmyuOnR5eqO47POdVNB5%2BYKBBUUhHeBNGrYOdoLMyLJRQujDtocLuwIXxNNc9y%2BIaC5o5wq9W%2FxK1PX43%2FHN%2BdTceXMF%2FCAiVqZrGXL9fqw5jbnTYdkbFL47V1Mq6TRKpYl1wTF7AaF1Cb0Y1A6QX1KKcUmF7CnEIkPOL03YXz8acvd2PqgWaiIpTIF6mbNHVEKLcPKX%2BsJyfUQipNaoGP3s9wcQNtpaneY5UcZ2whuS1ihPMv0%2FFFh%2FIxqsj%2F4DZKUV4ysbxF%2FZeJYQQvMwkkK5ULvEaRY7yxeD3v1AX0eqfOp0Qh5kiZXNEIHaJ28fzax%2FOdUyVv1AmLbMHEOZPf%2F64m5Vz7ByIdNaCPoO3D8SFcZyZfZ3IR7xTicvEGq2S8YCZZluw59FcVeQGly3i257CuJqCabSp27H4vcNbBB%2Bpmme%2BaAs9ztg8DSmImSy7iebEwuz6%2F1j6%2FBZUPEyLB%2FRKCTctpQUpa4nceld0RvJXGxvfl5dnkH2BPqN1q0BUBPz0Mt6UW78jQ8my1rm8yixQZSYR0c7xbKTrO3l2hkBfWODVztzJ0pblVHsG9m%2B8LUN9xCLPWREUkTSc7%2BF7rbtbqQhlvyhlChky2G4XZIQX48NrdRV7xJ6xXSiybYduaOMygvRfgHgoqR3O7hPbZ50%2BdZuKOipqRZzef4QQuVqyxtBpzuuKw0Cbl%2BQHstvaasVOa0LV7HhAmyBYFNpN2VOpItGn9YI%2FWfOUdGMm2umuk199P8BupnN4MQxwD7bRONafLl4QUoznQ0P3dWEVoaOxk8ml8uYfpu%2BuhYu2tiEP18dg77TRMCQxL0E37rj4Gd%2FQwMB2lBzI9TK%2FgD24BNd1J7nEbwYQb29NIW2iwXf1hlLbny3a9IF14%2BfH8A557W3FeO3STzd1rNYIV6N57WO31tPG9m17ffH1bziFU%2F5Jw6v98%2FejR2nPKwtBqbj2hFMF5bEefydbr%2F4J4Nk0%3D" id="w1_2_3_4_5_11_12"><mxCell style="rounded=1;whiteSpace=wrap;html=1;fontSize=11;fillColor=#c9b3dd;strokeColor=#4a2a78;fontColor=#201040;" vertex="1" parent="1"><mxGeometry x="2124" y="1195" width="280" height="108" as="geometry"/></mxCell></object><object label="Count soil animals&lt;br&gt;(~10^19 nematodes)&lt;br&gt;[1+2+3+4+5+11+12+13]&lt;br&gt;→ Wild insects (humane pesticides)&lt;br&gt;(Vasco Grilo)" tooltip="&lt;b&gt;parochial + far_away_humans + animals_somewhat + future_humans_matter_with_discounting + no_discounting_future_humans + animals_matter_a_lot + person_affecting_view + resilient_foods_beat_agi + soil_animals&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Grilo&#x27;s soil-animal accounting: ~10^19 soil nematodes, mites and springtails dominate the welfare effects of almost anything. Global-health charities raise food demand and cropland (~137 m^2-yr/$ for GiveWell top charities, ~1.11 kQALY/$ of soil-animal welfare change); with soil lives net-negative, that makes GiveWell&#x27;s top charities net-harmful, and soil/wild-invertebrate work dominates the slate. Only enters once invertebrates already count, so it requires animals_matter_a_lot. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 11 person_affecting_view → 12 resilient_foods_beat_agi → 13 soil_animals" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJyFVmtT6zYQ%2FSs7TDtNKAQ%2FAoR08oFHeEy5vQyX9k6HML6KvY7VK0seScakXP57V3aeJEy%2FKd7V2d2zZ1d53UkwZaWw5yrBnf7OwQEMBgN40IxLsApizf6d0qGSMCoDz%2B9CpbRInjlWUPlREIVRNzqMfD%2Fyg8gPoWWsKsAP2w5mJAnu1JgyLyxXEuKMUPvgQcG0ijPOhAP1TwLwIWU6YhWbRlmZM2nmhgCY5DkTJjIqxypjdm4JIS1tqXF2IcqZtaijitssSriJVSktl5O5exekWv0erd2eex0uws3gWCTUIqTvQ4HaKBmxNMW4hqmZmNsD0Gi44ChtlCqVmGiMzEZswhcuIRjFRTQLUzM0ZHEGbEkTN8DgbmozOqdcIFArlmZzANbRwJLE7FE86h%2BXaEDpGkzjPrHLcqTsuaHvNsOG%2BF8MMSbjGuM3iFVeKOMIWjjQXZkgIdIn3qRmLJMJE0oi5CQQ0YFvi%2F4Pn7%2B5VN11fCmIDrr4zESJoNIaYSmVTg12hsbCuJxC6cK4iwZXC%2BvDVy4SqtYQmIFW3Rokyo3lMU%2FQtBucq%2BEfw%2FvTh%2BEFjKcwQYmaWewU07lCMeF2jbBdMu5R%2F22TluOUkGqsC64pGGDdTyDC0TVD6QmxVWjqkZ7CmEKklAGd9%2BBsePn5fkhsaCZqhAr5JHNSIG6EcjOT8W9ND4WaS