r_a_lot + resilient_foods_beat_agi&lt;/b&gt;&lt;br&gt;&lt;br&gt;Denkenberger &amp; Pearce estimate ~98-99% confidence that marginal funding for resilient foods (feeding everyone through nuclear winter or an abrupt sunlight-reduction catastrophe) does more far-future good than marginal AGI-safety funding — it is more neglected and more tractable while buying the same astronomical future. The longtermist winner flips from AI safety to ALLFED. A within-longtermism reallocation, so it requires no_discounting_future_humans. || Chain: 0 parochial → 1 far_away_humans → 2 animals_somewhat → 3 future_humans_matter_with_discounting → 4 no_discounting_future_humans → 5 animals_matter_a_lot → 12 resilient_foods_beat_agi" link="https://www.squiggle-language.com/playground#code=eJx1Vm1z4jYQ%2Fis7TDuFDCHGkN4dHT6QhLxMuV4mx%2FWmEzKOsNdYPVnySHIcmst%2F78oGAsF8wnhXz749z8ovjQhjlgt7riJsDBonJzAcDmGqGZdgFYSa%2Fbekh0LCLPe9bh8KpUX0xLGAohv4QS%2FoB6dB14emsSqDrt9yADNJQCNj8jSzXEkIE8IbgAcZ0ypMOBMOrvvJhy7ETAesYMsgyVMmzdrgA5M8ZcIERqVYJMyuLT2Ic5trXB0IUmYt6qDgNgkibkKVS8vlYu3eB6m23wc7p9dep5twKzgWCLUJSfVpNFxwlDaIlYpMMEdmA7bgZaljFibA3urlBhjcLm1CzzEXCNTNN7M5AevqYVFk2gRMI%2BASDShdgmk8pjaxFCkNbui9TbDq4G%2BGSpdhifEHhCrNlHGVbhzorIyQEOkVNyWasUxGTCiJkNKMRQceNyMcPz26VN1xfM4wtHTwiYkcQcUlwtu0OyXYGRoL83wJuQvjDhrcLmwAo8nkcnxReV%2BN%2FxrfjabjC5gvYYESNbPYyZZrKmHE7U5bjsjYpnHZKrjrHCGVWBdcU36Acex%2BqK3oWq70gnqSaZqcXsKcQsQ85PTchrPx5Ze7MdWsmSgRCuSLxBGAOiCUI3fCH6tJCbWQStP04ZP3K5zfQFNpqu9YxccpW0hu8wjh7Mt0fN6ifIzKsz%2B5DROUF0wsb1F%2FMxEM4WUmATJUmcBrFBlGG4vX8U5dQK9z6nwKFGKOlMkVjcxBVC5et%2FLxus6ppCvqmIU2Z%2BKMyR9%2Fl5Nxrr0DkY5qoI%2Bg2YXjQ3CtmXydyUW0U4jLxeuvkvH8mWRpvOfQW1Xk%2BZQu4%2Bmew7oan2q2idixdzu%2Bs%2FY%2FUDeLbNfke56zfehTEjNZcBHN84XZ9fm98vnolz5MiBj3S%2FA3LSdBFCTadx6l3SF4K46N74uL0eQfYE%2BonRQyovgvD4NtqkU7NLQ8XcnzjWahIiORkDbFOwnRcfZuJUKWW%2BPYzK0jVqicdIdw7%2Bb7AtR3HMCsMVEhUdPRDn5UvJs12lBEm3IGkCKTzVpitogBXXht70Je8SesJCWW9WDbnDiM8Z34Bm7xUzma2yU0R58vW%2FWIOyyqhxzdfIYTOF9hjaXVmNFKw1ybhGcHYLe5Vw87pQldu3WPMEG2yLEeaYelDomU1vP30L4mt